Package prkmodel.statistics

Class DefaultDataCollector

java.lang.Object
prkmodel.statistics.DefaultDataCollector
All Implemented Interfaces:
DataCollector
public final class DefaultDataCollector extends Object implements DataCollector
Default implementation of the DataCollector interface for collecting data and statistics from the nervous system simulation. This class gathers various statistics about the state and activity of the nervous system and its components.
Since:
2024-07-03
Version:
